{"tid":1842460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有巴士公司曾經反對員工派口罩俾乘客","createTime":"2020-01-25T16:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T17:16:25.000Z","uid":63979,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c8837b624888030840cf979877284d8de7a5030a","tid":1842460,"uid":63979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:50:25.000Z","msg":"【無奈取消11月6日《全城口罩日》】 <br />\n<br />\n     本聯盟決定取消11月6日發起的《全城口罩日》；原因為有巴士公司向成員工會表示，現時為敏感時期，巴士員工不可以在車廂上派發口罩予乘客，公司亦會對參與員工「有所行動」；更一度表示「唔著公司製服，喺站頭(即巴士總站) 派，就唔理你哋」。本聯盟毫不明白，為何有巴士公司將「保乘客呼吸健康」的派發口罩宣傳日，與政治議題掛勾。<br />\n<br />\n     本聯盟曾經與民間組織【健康空氣行動】做巴士車箱空氣測試，巴士車廂內的空氣質素較室外差，空氣污染物二氧化氮的濃度高於世界衛生組織年均安全標準的3至4倍，詳情可參考相關媒體報導：<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/roadsidepollutants/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Froadsidepollutants%2F&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=d67d7555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/roadsidepollutants/</a><br />\n<br />\n     本聯盟所發起的《全城口罩日》是以乘客健康為出發點，但為了員工著想，本聯盟唯有無奈取消，希望香港人諒解。健康空氣，無罪！<br />\n<br />\n巴士業職工會聯盟<br />\n2019年11月5日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/189574754981356/posts/483484782257017/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F189574754981356%2Fposts%2F483484782257017%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=a82430c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/189574754981356/posts/483484782257017/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n聽聞果間係新巴城巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0d1f9b17e62bfbff1ed5cb5ad2832f5f4d8827","tid":1842460,"uid":63979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:53:08.000Z","msg":"搵人推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524